<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 2 (Xinhua) -- Iranian President Mohammad
Khatami today pledged to fight against cultural invasion by "a
minority" of countries in the world, the official news agency
IRNA reported.
</P>
<P>
Addressing Iranian officials in charge of cultural work
abroad, the 54-year-old president said "the big powers use their
technological capabilities to distort the news in line with their
own interests.".
</P>
