political and economic interests by controlling the mass media.
</P>
<P>
"Armed with the teachings of Islam, we should confront this
cultural invasion through binding ties with the thinkers and
scholars across the world," he noted.
</P>
<P>
He called on Iran's representatives to foreign countries to
try to establish strong links with the world nations as a means
of forging alliances.
</P>
<P>
