released.
</P>
<P>
The ten-part series contains more than two million Chinese
characters, over 1,200 photographs, and 87 film and TV fragments
in chronological order.
</P>
<P>
Ding Guangen, a member of the Political Bureau and Secretariat
of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of Chinese (CPC),
called today for better implementation of Deng's theory of
building socialism with Chinese characteristics to educate the
people.
</P>
<P>
