country, Deng was the chief architect of our country's socialist
reform and opening-up, and the founder of the theory of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics," Ding said.
</P>
<P>
It has been shown that the theory solves the question about the
destiny of China's socialism, he said.
</P>
<P>
The 15th National Congress of the CPC will start soon, he said,
and it will "hold high the banner of Deng's theory of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics and make strategic
arrangements for the trans-century development of our country's
reform, opening-up, and socialist modernization drive to propel
the cause of building socialism with Chinese characteristics into
the 21st century."
</P>
<P>
"We must closely unite around the CPC Central Committee with
Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core...and advance the cause of
building socialism with Chinese characteristics initiated by Deng
Xiaoping in an all-round way," he said. 
