<HEADLINE> Nigeria to Set Up Transitional Government </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, September 2 (Xinhua) -- Nigeria may set up a
transitional government to supervise the transition to civil rule
program of the military government of General Sani Abacha, the
Nigerian Tribune reported today.
</P>
<P>
